	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was looking at 15 watt soldering irons. I see they range from temperatures from 600 to 1000 degrees. Should I get one that works at lower temperatures? Should I get one that takes batteries or plugs in?
<br />
<br />Should I get a desoldering Iron?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


